even if you don't like it.

129
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,160
The Tiramisu cakes Chenchuan sells

130
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,720
are all made of the best materials.

131
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,320
The step of
softening the cheese alone...

132
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:33,960
You know it well.

133
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:35,760
Yeah.

134
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:38,360
I worked part-time in Chenchuan's shop.

135
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,040
I have to say,

136
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,080
Chenchuan is the best boss

137
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,280
I've ever had.

138
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,400
If you don't want to waste it,

139
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,120
you can stay here and enjoy it.

140
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,920
Did I say anything wrong?

141
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,160
Han Qilu

142
00:05:58,280 --> 00:06:02,840
is a big scoundrel who wastes things.

143
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:05,680
Draw a circle to curse you

144
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:08,560
for having nightmares tonight.

